title: STOOPS! There It Is! - Week 6 Reviewed
description:
We discuss:
- Why Mike Stoops Was Barely Making It On 950K a Year
- Why Spencer should shut the hell up about being happy because he doesn't know the meaning of pain
- The joy of watching Paul Johnson sit on a grudge for 12 damn years
- Mizzou/South Carolina was the most important game of the week because dear god, did you see half the bullshit that happened in that game
